*This paper was written using tools I don't own, on platforms I don't control, and will likely be stored on servers I cannot access. The irony is structural. The collapse is economic. The only question is whether we learn from it—or just click "Accept Terms of Service" and move on.*

**Published by the Department of Highly Unapproved Methods, 2025**

